RelatedSentence: The OSCE mission conducted a monitoring on troops contact line in the Tartar - Agdara highway of Azerbaijan ` s Tartar region on May 19 in accordance with the mandate of special envoy of the OSCE Chairman-in-Office .

Azerbaijan ` s Defense Ministry reported the monitoring has been held on the Azerbaijani side by field assistants of the Personal Representative of the OSCE Chairman-in-Office Jiri Aberle and Peter Svedberg .
